  "instructions": [
    "Heat copper-pot over medium heat. ",
    "Add water and orange juice, stirring to combine. ",
    "Bring mixture to a boil. ",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes. ",
    "Add flour and salt; stir to form dough. ",
    "Knead dough for 5 minutes. ",
    "Let rest for 1 hour. ",
    "Divide dough into 8 equal pieces. ",
    "Roll each into a ball. ",
    "Flatten into a disk. ",
    "Place a tablespoon of ground beef in center. ",
    "Fold empanada in half, pressing edges to seal. ",
    "Heat a tablespoon of oil in copper-pot over medium heat. ",
    "Cook empanadas 3-4 minutes per side. "
  ],
